20:19.920 --> 20:20.140
Yeah.

20:20.140 --> 20:22.340
It's just – you have to pick and choose.

20:22.340 --> 20:35.920
And I think that's one reason why you don't have academics in the past looking into UFOs, because why spend time on something that's probably nonsensical when you can be spending time on something that is probably going to pay off?

20:36.000 --> 20:38.540
